<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:08:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列总检察长表示，飞马委员会无视高等法院的命令，要求提供未决案件的详细信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-pegasus-commission-asked-for-details-on-pending-cases/0000018e-2de7-d2cd-a58f-ade7fb4b0000</link><description>总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉 (Gali Baharav-Miara) 告诉最高法院，调查委员会提出的请求违反了法院命令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-pegasus-commission-asked-for-details-on-pending-cases/0000018e-2de7-d2cd-a58f-ade7fb4b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的红线：为什么美国可能几天后就会暂停对以色列的武器销售</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-u-s-could-be-days-away-from-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel/0000018e-2da3-d12e-ad8e-edbb738c0000</link><description>经过几个月的猜测，美国与以色列的关系已经达到了一个转折点，随着美国总统乔·拜登争先恐后地向加沙提供更多人道主义援助，这一时刻可能最终会在本月晚些时候到来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 15:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-u-s-could-be-days-away-from-suspending-arms-sales-to-israel/0000018e-2da3-d12e-ad8e-edbb738c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列本古里安大学拒绝性别隔离校园以迎合极端正统派的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-rejects-gender-segregation-proposal-for-new-campus/0000018e-2de8-dd22-a5fe-7ffbd2d40000</link><description>尽管该提案的支持者认为，性别隔离的校园将使极端正统派人士能够接受高等教育，但反对者表示，这“违背了平等的价值观”，并有使性别隔离正常化的风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 15:06:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-rejects-gender-segregation-proposal-for-new-campus/0000018e-2de8-dd22-a5fe-7ffbd2d40000</guid></item><item><title>美国进步团体首次发起针对 AIPAC“黑钱”的此类活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-progressive-groups-launch-first-of-its-kind-campaign-against-aipacs-dark-money/0000018e-2d68-d468-a9ff-2ff9fa510000</link><description>由二十多个进步组织组成的“拒绝 AIPAC”联盟表示，计划通过选举、政治、数字和组织策略来对抗 AIPAC 及其超级 PAC</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-progressive-groups-launch-first-of-its-kind-campaign-against-aipacs-dark-money/0000018e-2d68-d468-a9ff-2ff9fa510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人的斋月之旅被取消，这是团结犹太人和巴勒斯坦人的难得机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-03-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ramadan-tours-a-rare-chance-to-unite-jews-and-palestinians-are-cancelled/0000018e-2939-dc52-abff-69bb49240000</link><description>随着加沙战争的激烈进行，“目前还不清楚现在作为游客进入清真寺是否正确，”一位联合以色列犹太人和巴勒斯坦人的斋月旅游经营者说。但圣月如何成为如此爆炸性的问题呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-03-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ramadan-tours-a-rare-chance-to-unite-jews-and-palestinians-are-cancelled/0000018e-2939-dc52-abff-69bb49240000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席谴责将军未经授权拆除加沙大学大楼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-reprimands-general-for-unauthorized-demolition-of-gaza-university-building/0000018e-2d12-d152-ad8e-2dfa03550000</link><description>以色列军方表示，虽然哈马斯将加沙城的以色列大学大楼用于军事目的，但它是在未经适当授权的情况下被拆除的。 10 月 7 日，希勒姆将军下令炮击贝埃里基布兹的一座房屋，以色列人质被关押在那里，目前正在接受以色列国防军调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 12:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-reprimands-general-for-unauthorized-demolition-of-gaza-university-building/0000018e-2d12-d152-ad8e-2dfa03550000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察在斋月的第一个晚上阻止数百名巴勒斯坦人进入阿克萨清真寺，并用警棍殴打信徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-police-block-hundreds-of-palestinians-from-al-aqsa-on-ramadans-first-night/0000018e-2d17-dc45-a7ef-6ddf8a200000</link><description>对斋月首次祈祷的限制与总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡最近允许礼拜自由的承诺相矛盾。过去几天，警方对巴勒斯坦活动人士和记者发出了数十项限制令，禁止他们进入大院</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:18:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-police-block-hundreds-of-palestinians-from-al-aqsa-on-ramadans-first-night/0000018e-2d17-dc45-a7ef-6ddf8a200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列房地产博览会在犹太人聚集的新泽西小镇吸引了数百名亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-real-estate-fair-draws-hundreds-of-protesters-in-heavily-jewish-n-j-town/0000018e-2cba-d152-ad8e-2dfa9ecd0000</link><description>数百名警察在场，以防止抗议者与犹太居民在活动中发生冲突，该活动在一定程度上促进了西岸的房地产发展</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:15:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-real-estate-fair-draws-hundreds-of-protesters-in-heavily-jewish-n-j-town/0000018e-2cba-d152-ad8e-2dfa9ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总统赫尔佐格在阿姆斯特丹会见荷兰极右翼反伊斯兰党领袖基尔特·威尔德斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-11/ty-article/israeli-president-meets-dutch-far-right-anti-islam-party-leader-wilders-in-amsterdam/0000018e-2d29-dc45-a7ef-6dfd89610000</link><description>威尔德斯主张荷兰“去伊斯兰化”，主张将荷兰大使馆迁至耶路撒冷并关闭荷兰驻拉马拉外交机构</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 11:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-11/ty-article/israeli-president-meets-dutch-far-right-anti-islam-party-leader-wilders-in-amsterdam/0000018e-2d29-dc45-a7ef-6dfd89610000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙人质与哈马斯的谈判在斋月开始时陷入困境，以色列不排除达成协议的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/start-of-ramadan-target-date-for-hostage-deal-arrives-with-no-deal-on-the-horizon/0000018e-2a16-d682-a9df-ebbe83f10000</link><description>一位外国官员表示，双方都在互相较量。另一位人士表示，“我们的假设是最终会达成协议。”哈马斯领导人哈尼亚表示，以色列没有承诺停止战斗并允许流离失所的加沙人从南部返回北部</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/start-of-ramadan-target-date-for-hostage-deal-arrives-with-no-deal-on-the-horizon/0000018e-2a16-d682-a9df-ebbe83f10000</guid></item><item><title>美国建造的港口可以将以色列变成加沙警察部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/the-american-aid-port-in-gaza-could-turn-idf-into-conquering-and-policing-force/0000018e-2b12-dc45-a7ef-6bdfb5160000</link><description>该港口可能会免除以色列对加沙人道主义局势的责任，但如果没有商定的授权，混乱的风险就会增加</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/the-american-aid-port-in-gaza-could-turn-idf-into-conquering-and-policing-force/0000018e-2b12-dc45-a7ef-6bdfb5160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在核实哈马斯高级指挥官是否在以色列国防军对加沙的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article-live/gaza-offical-only-hamas-has-the-ability-to-distribute-aid-from-bidens-gaza-port/0000018e-2b4f-dc52-abff-6bcf451b0000</link><description>以色列正在检查哈马斯激进组织二号人物马尔万·伊萨是否在一次袭击中身亡。 据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，美国相信以色列近期不会在拉法行动。阿克萨大院 ■ 加沙官员警告说，只有哈马斯才有能力监督援助物资的分配 ■ 美国推动战斗暂停两到四天，以恢复协议谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article-live/gaza-offical-only-hamas-has-the-ability-to-distribute-aid-from-bidens-gaza-port/0000018e-2b4f-dc52-abff-6bcf451b0000</guid></item><item><title>七名阿拉伯裔以色列男子被指控策划对犹太以色列人发动恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/seven-arab-israeli-men-accused-of-planning-terror-attacks-on-jewish-israelis/0000018e-29fa-dc52-abff-69fa59a70000</link><description>这七人来自北部城市萨赫宁，据称购买武器并接受训练，目的是在战争爆发时攻击犹太公民和士兵。该小组后来由一名自称哈马斯成员的加沙人指挥</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:10:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/seven-arab-israeli-men-accused-of-planning-terror-attacks-on-jewish-israelis/0000018e-29fa-dc52-abff-69fa59a70000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年，阿拉伯裔以色列人的谋杀率创下历史新高。今年的步伐正在加快</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-murders-on-track-for-another-record-breaking-year/0000018e-29fa-d682-a9df-e9fe43080000</link><description>《国土报》报道称，今年迄今已有 36 名以色列阿拉伯人被谋杀，而 2023 年同期为 31 人，受害者总数为 299 人</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 22:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-murders-on-track-for-another-record-breaking-year/0000018e-29fa-d682-a9df-e9fe43080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左翼将在拉马拉宣布胜利，签署两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lefts-victory-photo-will-be-in-muqata/0000018e-2994-d099-a1ff-3bd6d7ed0000</link><description>以色列左派现在有机会提出一种替代刀剑生活的选择，并再次发挥作用</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 21:38:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lefts-victory-photo-will-be-in-muqata/0000018e-2994-d099-a1ff-3bd6d7ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公布欧洲歌唱大赛参赛作品《飓风》</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-unveils-hurricane-its-entry-for-the-eurovision-song-contest/0000018e-2a27-d682-a9df-ebaf12ed0000</link><description>这首歌由 Eden Golan 演唱，将代表以色列参加五月在瑞典举行的欧洲歌唱大赛。周日早些时候，一名支持巴勒斯坦的用户在网上泄露了这首歌的预录，标题是“以色列正在实施种族灭绝”</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 21:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-unveils-hurricane-its-entry-for-the-eurovision-song-contest/0000018e-2a27-d682-a9df-ebaf12ed0000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，以色列的 GPS 干扰令黎巴嫩边境的约会应用程序陷入混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/israels-gps-jamming-confuses-dating-apps-on-lebanese-border-report-says/0000018e-29d6-d682-a9df-e9fec4370000</link><description>据 Business Insider 报道，使用 GPS 位置的应用程序受到以色列军方为阻止黎巴嫩袭击而进行的 GPS 干扰的影响。因此，2 月份出现在黎巴嫩 Tinder 上的个人资料中有 60-62% 是以色列国民</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 20:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/israels-gps-jamming-confuses-dating-apps-on-lebanese-border-report-says/0000018e-29d6-d682-a9df-e9fec4370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军法律顾问称，定居者委员会没收巴勒斯坦人的牛群是非法的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/settler-councils-confiscating-palestinians-herds-is-illegal-says-military-legal-adviser/0000018e-27e2-d1b8-a5de-e7fe17300000</link><description>以色列国防军西岸法律顾问表示，该委员会执行的章程仅适用于以色列人，不适用于巴勒斯坦人。四名巴勒斯坦牧民的代表请求以色列高等法院释放这些动物并退还理事会收取的款项</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 19:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/settler-councils-confiscating-palestinians-herds-is-illegal-says-military-legal-adviser/0000018e-27e2-d1b8-a5de-e7fe17300000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判：尽管总理要求推迟，但官员作证的日期已确定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-dates-set-for-officials-testimony-despite-pms-request-to-postpone/0000018e-2987-d7d3-abce-69afc0f10000</link><description>法官们并未正式拒绝内塔尼亚胡推迟作证的请求，但通过安排两次作证基本上否定了内塔尼亚胡的要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 19:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-dates-set-for-officials-testimony-despite-pms-request-to-postpone/0000018e-2987-d7d3-abce-69afc0f10000</guid></item><item><title>科学发现巨蛇新物种：北方绿森蚺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-10/ty-article/science-recognizes-new-species-of-giant-snake-the-northern-green-anaconda/0000018e-2909-dbcf-abee-39d967280000</link><description>事实证明，南美洲的巨型绿蛇不是一种，而是两种。在截然不同的地形中发现的多种黄色水蚺就是其中之一</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 18:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-10/ty-article/science-recognizes-new-species-of-giant-snake-the-northern-green-anaconda/0000018e-2909-dbcf-abee-39d967280000</guid></item></channel></rss>